summary: Okay so of course not all firbolgs know each other... but what if it turns out Pumat and Caduceus are brothers? Granted, Deuce...
body:
Okay so of course not all firbolgs know each other… but what if it turns out Pumat and Caduceus are brothers? Granted, Deuce didn’t recognize Pumat’s name, but what if he just changed it.

Like, once the Nein are back in Zadash, they take him to the Vulnerable Vagrant, expecting him to freak over there being 4 Pumats. But as soon as Caduceus gets a good look at Pumat, he’s just like “Hey, *Insert Embarrassing Name Here*! Haven’t seen you since you left home something odd years ago!”

Also family discounts

summary: Hey guys, I’m running a 5e campaign and the party is currently in the feywild
body:
Hey guys, I’m running a 5e campaign and the party is currently in the feywild

If anyone has any advice and/or tips for running a campaign in the feywild including encounters (combat or otherwise) please message your ideas to me!!

The party came to the feywild by total accident and so far have run into a gorgon artifact and a pack of 3 hill giants. I’m accepting any and all advice from you guys! 😁
